    <svcproc id="s26510.2.7" graphiccount="1">
        <title>EGR Valve Assembly (Exhaust Gas Recirculation)</title>
        <figure id="e3001108" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figJ09/J09020.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px" box="no"/>
            <caption>EGR valve assembly</caption>
        </figure>
        <para>The EGR valve assembly is located on the front of the intake manifold behind the air inlet. The ECM sends
            a desired position signal to the EGR drive module. The EGR drive module controls the EGR valve. The EGR
            drive module sends a position signal to the ECM for diagnostics.
        </para>
    </svcproc>
